          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Let NHTSA Enforce Automated Vehicle Driving Regulations Act or the LEAD'R Act</strong></p> <p>This bill provides for federal preemption of state laws regulating highly automated vehicles and automated driving systems (or components of such systems). A state may not enact a law in this area unless such law is identical to federal standards.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-07-26T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <actionDate>2017-07-26</actionDate>
        </item>
